"Administration menu. Clicking on the Administration menu opens a page (see "
"screen image, below) from which each of these specific administrative tasks "
"can be accessed by clicking on the appropriate button. Note that the button "
"labelled \"Organizations\" will remain disabled by default until the GBIF "
"registration options have been set."
msgstr ""

