"If it is the same throughout the dataset, consider using a static mapping of "
"the term and value. See the Darwin Core Archive How-to Guide at "
"http://links.gbif.org/gbif_dwca_how_to_guide_en_v1 for details on mapping "
"global values."
msgstr ""

