"events and occurrences in the same dataset. The current work around requires "
"publishers to publish separate datasets. Note OBIS is prototyping an "
"Extended Measurement or Facts Extension that could also help overcome this "
"limitation. Discussion on this prototype extension is taking place in GitHub "
"here. However, issues raised that this prototype extension does not "
"explicitly make it clear if the measurement or fact relates to an occurrence "
"or an event. One alternative is to add resourceID (and perhaps "
"resourceType?) instead of adding eventID (and occurrenceID) as attribute to "
