#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:122
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Records** - the number of rows of data in the core data file of the last "
"published Darwin Core Archive for the resource. For resources having data in "
"one or more extension files, the number links to the Data Records page on "
"the resource homepage showing a breakdown of record counts by extension.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:123
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Last modified** - either the date the resource was created or the date on "
"which the data or metadata were last modified, whichever is more recent.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:124
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Last publication** - the date the resource was last published.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:125
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Next publication** - the date the resource will be published next.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ===
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:126
#, no-wrap
msgid "RSS feed"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:128
msgid ""
"The IPT supports syndication via RSS for those who wish to monitor when new "
"resource versions get published, and how resources change over time. In fact "
"each time a new resource version is broadcast, it will include a summary of "
"what changed since the last version (assuming the publisher entered a change "
"summary, otherwise it defaults to the resource description). The RSS feed is "
"accessible by clicking on the link provided below the list of public hosted "
"resources. The RSS feed can be read in any standard RSS client."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ===
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:129
#, no-wrap
msgid "Registered resource inventory"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:131
msgid ""
"The IPT provides a simple JSON inventory of all registered resources. This "
"feature isn't shown on the user interface. To view simply append "
"`/inventory/dataset` to the IPT public URL, "
"e.g. https://ipt.gbif.org/inventory/dataset. GBIF uses this inventory to "
"monitor whether it is properly indexing resources by comparing the target "
"and indexed record counts."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ===
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:132
#, no-wrap
msgid "Resource homepage"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:134
msgid ""
"The resource homepage is aimed at external users of a resource. The homepage "
"lists all the metadata about a selected version of a resource, provides "
"links to download the version's data/metadata, and displays the resource's "
"version history."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:136
msgid ""
"To view the resource homepage, user can click on the name link in the list "
"of resources on the Home page. Another way to get to the resource's homepage "
"is using its DOI: when a resource is assigned a DOI via the IPT, it always "
"resolves to its homepage."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:138
msgid ""
"Please note only a user having the Admin role or one of the Manager roles "
"can edit a resource's metadata. To learn more, please refer to the "
"information under the \"Edit an existing resource\" heading in the \"Manage "
"Resources Menu\" section."
msgstr ""

#. type: Target for macro image
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:139
#, no-wrap
msgid "ipt2/home/IPTHomeMetadataOverview.png"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ====
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:141
#, no-wrap
msgid "Version history"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:143
msgid ""
"The version history table lists all published versions of the resource, "
"enabling users to track changes to the resource over time and download "
"previous versions' data/metadata. Please note, the IPT's Archival Mode must "
"be turned on in order for old versions of DwC-A to be stored (see the "
"xref:administration.adoc#_configure_ipt_settings[Configure IPT Settings] "
"section). Only versions that are publicly accessible can be viewed by "
"external users, whereas admins and resource managers can see all "
"versions. For explanations of the table columns, refer to the information "
"below."
msgstr ""

#. type: Target for macro image
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:144
#, no-wrap
msgid "ipt2/home/IPTVersionHistoryTable.png"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:147
msgid "Following are explanations of the table columns:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:149
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Version** - the published version's version number, which uses the "
"major_version.minor_version format. The version of the resource homepage "
"currently being viewed is clearly indicated. To open a specific version's "
"homepage, click on the version number. **Note**: A major version change "
"compared to the last published version indicates that a scientifically "
"significant change has taken place.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:150
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Published on** - the date the published version was released.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:151
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Records** - the number of records the published version contains.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:152
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Change summary** - a summary of what has changed since the last published "
"version.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:153
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**DOI handle** - the DOI handle assigned to the published version. **Note**: "
"If the DOI is different from the DOI of the last published version, this "
"indicates that a scientifically significant change has been done to the "
"resource.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/modules/ROOT/pages/quick-reference-guide.adoc:154
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Last modified by** - the IPT user that last modified the published "
"version.\n"
msgstr ""

